Author: annielovesbacon
Text: AH my therapist did this to me too (essentially threatened to send me to inpatient if I kept losing) and I was scared too!! I managed to avoid it tho, god bless. I knew she wasn’t trying to get rid of me, I get the ethics of it.   also... “nut up or shut up” bro I’m dying laughing imagining my therapist saying that to me
